	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Observande pater, <persName type="auto_name">S. Philippus</persName> parat expeditionem contra nostros in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l640">Flandria</placeName>, et iam appulerunt <placeName ref="l1121" cert="high">Genuam</placeName> septem millia Hispanorum; hybernabunt in ducatu <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanensi</placeName> primo vere profecturi in Flandriam.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In dies etiam expectatur <persName type="auto_name">Philippus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">quę certa sunt scribo, reliqua relinquo vulgo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Propter persecutionem, quę fervet in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italia</placeName>, subinde aliqui ad nos confugiunt.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valemus omnes; precor deum ut te quoque et omnes filios diu conservet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l96">Cl[avennae]</placeName> 12. decembris 66.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p4037" cert="high">H[ieronymus] Z[anchus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Misissem et ad te et ad reliquos fratres, qui me soliti estis novis vestris lucubrationibus donare, exemplaria aliquot mei libri grati animi ergo; sed nullum adhuc ad me missum est.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bonam ergo meam voluntatem amplectimini.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henr[ico] Bullingero</persName>, ecclesię Tigurinę patri dignissimo et observandissimo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tigurum.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
